TextAlign="Center">DIRECTIONS</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">9. <Tab />Directions</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><!--Heading:COLLECTION AND DISCLOSURE OF INFORMATION--><Para TopMargin="16" Size="9" Leading="10" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center">COLLECTION AND DISCLOSURE OF INFORMATION</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">10. <Tab />Assistance to Minister</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">11. <Tab />Disclosure</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">12. <Tab />Foreign states</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">13. <Tab />Minister of Transport</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">14. <Tab />Canada Border Services Agency</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><!--Heading:ADMINISTRATIVE RECOURSE--><Para TopMargin="16" Size="9" Leading="10" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center">ADMINISTRATIVE RECOURSE</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">15. <Tab />Application to Minister</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><!--Heading:APPEALS--><Para TopMargin="16" Size="9" Leading="10" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center">APPEALS</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">16. <Tab />Decisions under this Act</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0">17. <Tab />Protecti